      <title>一系列错误让拜登对奥斯汀一无所知四天</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/series-of-errors-left-biden-in-dark-about-austin-for-four-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，五角大楼未能通知总统乔·拜登，他的国防部长已住院四天，这是一系列错误的结果，包括对劳埃德·奥斯汀的意愿感到困惑以及他的幕僚长生病。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/series-of-errors-left-biden-in-dark-about-austin-for-four-days</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 03:38:21 GMT</pubDate>
